createPlayList

public ArrayList<Track> createPlayList(int minRating,
                                       int duration)
A method to create a random playlist and implement the required functions. The user should give a required minimum rating. Tracks in the playlist should have a rating no lower than the minimum rating. The user should give a required duration. The total length of the tracks in the playlist should be no longer than the duration.

Parameters:
minRating - The required minimum rating of the tracks.
duration - The required total running time of the playlist.

public void importTracks()
The method to import real mp3 files in the "MP3" folder. Add the mp3 files into the allTracks arraylist and get a list of albums.
